        <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-top:20px; max-width:800px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;">Three moments of money that fluX One connects — with intelligence integrated at every step.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="showcase-layout sr fade-in d1">
        <!-- Columna Izquierda: Tabs Interactivas -->
